  Locus:
    Page: 330
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Nature
---
Nature has devised a grand plan leading toward perfection. Life itself is
one lengthy march to such an ideal using death as the process by which the
tainted and the imperfect are recycled into another more enduring form.
